  "title": "Program Manager (Semiconductor & Medical)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a listed company in Precision Manufacturing industry. Due to business needs, they are now recruiting a Program Manager to be part of their Project Team. They are located in the East Area - easily accessible.</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Duties of Program Manager:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Project Planning &amp; Execution:</strong> Develop and manage project plans, timelines, resources, and budgets to ensure on-time, on-scope delivery.</li>\n  <li><strong>Team Leadership:</strong> Lead cross-functional teams and foster collaboration.</li>\n  <li><strong>Stakeholder Management:</strong> Serve as main contact for clients, suppliers, and internal teams.</li>\n  <li><strong>Risk &amp; Quality:</strong> Identify risks, implement mitigation strategies, and ensure deliverables meet quality standards.</li>\n  <li><strong>Budget &amp; Reporting:</strong> Monitor budgets, maintain documentation, and provide regular updates to management.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min Diploma in Mechanical Engineering or related field</li>\n  <li>At least 5 - 10 years of experience in semiconductor, precision or medical devices contract manufacturing industry</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click <strong>APPLY NOW</strong> or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Email Address: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></li>\n  <li>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.</li>\n  <li>EA License No. 19C9682</li>\n  <li>EA Reg. No. R22108850 (Chan Mun Mun)</li>\n</ul>",
